#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to Play"
msgstr "Nola jokatu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The player is presented with a blank board, and a list of numbers for each "
"row and column. These numbers represent how runs are organized within any "
"given row or column. For example, a number sequence of <quote>4 8 3</quote> "
"would mean there are sets of four, eight, and three filled cells, in that "
"order, with at least one blank cell between successive groups. The objective "
"of the game is to use these hints to uncover the actual solution, and do "
"this as quickly as possible."
msgstr ""
"Jokalariari jokaleku huts bat aurkezten zaio, eta zenbaki zerrenda bat "
"errenkada eta zutabe bakoitzeko. Zenbaki hauek adierazten dute gelaxka "
"multzoak nola antolatzen diren errenkada eta zutabeetan. Adibidez, <quote>4 "
"8 3</quote> zenbaki sekuentziak adieraziko lukete lau, zortzi eta hiru "
"gelaxka talde beteta daudela, hurrenkera horretan, taldeen artean gutxienez "
"gela huts bat dagoelarik. Taldearen helburua da argibide hauek erabiltzea "
"ebazpenera iristeko, eta hori guztiak ahalik eta denbora gutxiena erabiliz."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A left-click (un)marks a cell as occupied, while a right click (un)marks a "
"cell as empty. Dragging may be used to mark several cells in a row or column "
"in one go. The elapsed time is displayed in the status bar, and an overview "
"of the game board is located in the upper left corner. A game is completed "
"once all occupied cells have been marked correctly."
msgstr ""
"Ezkerreko klik batek gelaxka bat okupatuta dagoela (des)markatzen du, "
"eskuineko-klik batek gela hutsik dagoela (des)markatzen du. Arrastatzea "
"erabil daiteke errenkada edo zutabe batean ekintza bakarrarekin gelaxka bat "
"baino gehiago markatzeko. Igarotako denbora egoera barran azaltzen da, eta "
"jokalekuaren gainbegirada bat goiko ezker izkinan. Jokoa osatu da "
"okupatutako gelaxka guztiak ondo markatu direnean."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The current placement of boxes and crosses (referred to as 'states' from now "
"on) can be saved at any time. Saving a new state does not overwrite previous "
"saved states. Restoring a state always returns to the most recently saved "
"state. This can be repeated until no more saved states remain. The number of "
"actions since the latest saved state is displayed in the status bar."
msgstr ""
"Kutxa eta gurutzeen uneko kokapena (aurrerantzean 'egoera' esango zaie) une "
"orotan gorde daiteke. Egoera berri bat gordetzeak ez du gordetako aurreko "
"egoerarik ezabatzen. Egoera batera lehengoratzea beti itzultzen du gordetako "
"egoera berrienera. Hau errepikatu daiteke gordetako egoera gehiago ez dagoen "
"arte. Gordetako azken egoeratik egindako ekintza kopurua azaltzen da egoera-"
"barran."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:82
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&picmi; includes two game modes. Random puzzles (generated by selecting "
#| "<guilabel>New</guilabel> from the menu) are generated according to the "
#| "selected difficulty settings. Alternatively, the included preset puzzles "
#| "can be played by selecting <guilabel>Load</guilabel>."
msgid ""
"&picmi; includes two game modes. Random puzzles (generated by selecting the "
"<menuchoice><shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> menu item) are generated according to the selected difficulty "
"settings. Alternatively, the included preset puzzles can be played by "
"selecting the <menuchoice><shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Load…</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"&picmi;-ek bi joko modu ditu. Ausazko buruhaustekoak (menuan "
"<guilabel>Berria</guilabel> hautatuta) sortzen dira hautatutako zailtasun "
"ezarpenak erabiliz. Beste aukera bat aurrezarritako buruhaustekoekin "
"jokatzea da, <guilabel>Zamatu</guilabel> hautatu behar da horretarako."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Rules, Strategies and Tips"
msgstr "Jokoaren arauak, estrategiak eta argibideak"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rules"
msgstr "Arauak"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The number sequence in a row or column provides certain information about "
"the count of occupied cells and their arrangement within a row or column."
msgstr ""
"Errenkada edo zutabe batean adierazten den zenbaki sekuentziak okupatutako "
"gelaxken eta haien antolamenduaren gaineko informazioa ematen du."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A number represents the length of a connected run of occupied cells on the "
"board. This run either has at least one empty cell on each side or is "
"located directly on the board edge."
msgstr ""
"Zenbaki batek jokalekuan jarraian okupatutako gelaxka kopurua adierazten du. "
"Jarraitasun honek gutxienez gelaxka huts bat dauka albo banatan, edo "
"jokalekuaren muturretako batean kokatuta dago."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additionally, a number sequence shows the order of these runs within a row "
"or column."
msgstr ""
"Gainera, zenbaki sekuentzia batek errenkada edo zutabe bateko bloke "
"sekuentzien ordena erakusten du."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Prevent mistakes:</guilabel> option applies only to games with "
"<guimenu>Custom</guimenu> difficulty."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:99
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "When the <guilabel>Prevent Mistakes</guilabel> option is enabled, it is "
#| "not possible to incorrectly mark a cell as occupied - instead, penalty "
#| "time is added to the timer. The penalty is increased with each mistake "
#| "made."
msgid ""
"When the <guilabel>Prevent mistakes:</guilabel> option is enabled, it is not "
"possible to incorrectly mark a cell as occupied - instead, penalty time is "
"added to the timer. The penalty is increased with each mistake made."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Saihestu akatsak</guilabel> aukera gaituta dagoenean, ezin da "
"gelaxka bat okupatu zuzena ez bada - horren ordez zigor denbora bat gehitzen "
"da. Zigorra handitu egiten da egindako akats bakoitzeko."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:100
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If <guilabel>Prevent Mistakes</guilabel> is disabled, there is no "
#| "feedback whether a cell has been marked correctly, and there is no "
#| "penalty for making mistakes."
msgid ""
"If <guilabel>Prevent mistakes:</guilabel> option is disabled, there is no "
"feedback whether a cell has been marked correctly, and there is no penalty "
"for making mistakes."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Saihestu akatsak</guilabel> desgaituta badago, ez du ezerk "
"adierazten gelaxka bat ondo markatu den, eta ez da zigorrik ezartzen akatsak "
"egiteagatik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:101
#, no-c-format
msgid "The game will stop once all occupied cells have been marked correctly."
msgstr "Jokoa geldituko da okupatutako gelaxka guztiak ondo markatu direnean."

